        " عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"مَا أَدَرْتَ عَلَيْهِ لِسَانَكَ فَأَخْرَجْتَهُ فَابْلَعْهُ وَ مَا أَخْرَجْتَهُ بِالْخِلاَلِ فَارْمِ بِهِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4262 - Imam (as) said: \"Whatever you roll around with your tongue and remove, swallow it, and whatever you remove with a toothpick, discard it.\""
        ]
